## TransformOptions.isBuiltInComponent property

If the pairing runtime provides additional built-in elements, use this to mark them as built-in so the compiler will generate component vnodes for them.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
isBuiltInComponent?: (tag: string) => symbol | void;
```
